title: caffe2 ONNX import  Upsample(mode=bilinear)-> UpsampleBilinear
body_html:
There are two types of ONNX Upsample (mode=nearest) and Upsample(mode=linear)
Caffe2 used to import all ONNX Upsample to ResizeNearest
This PR adds support for:

  • ONNX import
    Upsample(mode=linear) -> UpsampleBilinear,
    Upsample(mode=nearest) -> ResizeNearest
  • ONNX export of the above two caffe2 operators
  • a unit-test case is added to verify bidirectional translation.

body:
There are two types of ONNX [Upsample](https://github.com/onnx/onnx/blob/master/docs/Operators.md#Upsample
) (mode=nearest) and Upsample(mode=linear)
Caffe2 used to import all ONNX Upsample to ResizeNearest
This PR adds support for:
* ONNX import
  Upsample(mode=linear) -> UpsampleBilinear,
  Upsample(mode=nearest) -> ResizeNearest
* ONNX export of the above two caffe2 operators
* a unit-test case is added to verify bidirectional translation.
